{
  "stem": "13690.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "How to bring in food to one of the various remote places where everything, that-- that a cup of water was a problem.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And to-- and to come up with that idea of saving Jews, and then come and go out and scaring his, so to say, his people-- it was a great idea.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we decided.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he said, 'I want you to go into each house, not to ask for anything.' Usually, the partisans in the past used to come into houses asking for food, for-- for chickens, for all kinds of means of food to be able to feed the partisans.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we did not ask for anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We did not want anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were really the good partisans, so to say.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did not want anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what did we want to do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when Eli walked in, into a house, he just asked, 'What is the name of this household, and how many people live in that household?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in case of an invasion of the troops, how many people would they able to station here?' That's about all, and wishing them all the best.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How-- did all of you walk in with Eli, or just Eli alone?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If we would have walked in with my other two uncles, they would definitely see that they are Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's no two ways about it, even including myself, which I was an invalid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was barely walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I was already a few months later-- I was barely walking properly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I was-- so he said no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, 'I will guide you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm walking with you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only Eli will go in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was not Eli.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ignacz. ?] And Uncle Joe, he will go in.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
